## Data
The gridded precipitation and temperature dataset (IMDAA) for India can be found at https://rds.ncmrwf.gov.in/datasets.
While the values of global climate indices are available at https://psl.noaa.gov/enso/dashboard.html. 
The SPEI package (available at https://github.com/sbegueria/SPEI) was used to calculate the SPEI-3 values.
